## ðŸ§ª Practical: Writing a YARA Rule

**Sample File:**
```bash
echo "This is a test with HelloWorld inside." > sample.txt
Rule File â€“ rule.yar:
   rule HelloWorldRule {
    meta:
        description = "Detects HelloWorld string"
        author = "MyName"
    strings:
        $a = "HelloWorld"
    condition:
        $a
}
Command to scan:
  yara rule.yar sample.txt

